OL,6,F"You don't get a chance like this very
OL,7,Foften, so when the opportunity comes
OL,8,Fup you grab it with both hands," he
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,F"Now we have this piece, it's about
OL,12,Fthe size of your hand but it's a 100%
OL,13,Fconnection that you can almost reach
OL,14,Finto the past and touch these events
OL,15,Fthat have affected us so recently,"
OL,16,Fexplained Dr O'Neill.
OL,18,FThe museum also has a scaled mock-up
OL,19,Fof the bomb measuring 2.03 metres in
OL,20,Fheight.
